author: doll
msg: Added in a new RouteManager for the samplecontainer. This converts the setstate, dumpstate and setevilness calls to use the restful code instead of the old json wire format code. (with tests) It also makes the old StateFileDataHandler obsolete.

To make this easy, I added a SimpleJsonAdapter. This class abstracts away some of abderas very xml notions and makes a json only handler much simpler to write. This change also moves the SocialRouteManager injections out of a method and into the constructor.
